<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ universityName }} University</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
        }

        main {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1em 0;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Christ University</h1>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>Welcome to Christ University!</h2>
            <p>Explore a world of knowledge and opportunities at {{ universityName }} University. Our commitment to excellence in education and research makes us a leading institution in the region.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Discover Your Potential</h2>
            <p>At {{ universityName }} University, we strive to empower our students to reach their full potential. Our diverse academic programs and experienced faculty provide a rich learning environment.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Campus Life</h2>
            <p>Immerse yourself in a vibrant campus life filled with student activities, clubs, and events. Build lasting connections with peers and engage in extracurricular activities that complement your academic journey.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; {{ currentYear }} {{ universityName }} University. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>
